  Your account won't be created until you access the link above and set your password.
%p All entries are $10 and must be paid by this Thursday at Noon Eastern.
%p
  Just a reminder, after you accept the invitation you can login in with your email address and password at
  \#{link_to root_url, root_url}.
%p Good Luck!
